Class IssueOrderPhase

java.lang.Object
Controller.Phases.Phase
Controller.Phases.PlayGamePhase
Controller.Phases.SubPhases.PlayMainPhase
Controller.Phases.SubPhases.IssueOrderPhase
public class IssueOrderPhase extends PlayMainPhase
Represents the phase where players issue orders during game play. In this phase, players can issue various types of orders, including deploying armies, advancing, bombing, blockading, airlifting, negotiating, and committing to orders. This phase allows players to issue orders, and the command handling is delegated to the player command handler.
